metadata.name: Scarab Ray
metadata.description: As you gaze upon Scarab Ray, you'll be struck by the beetle's shimmering exoskeleton, which seems to emulate the sun's rays themselves. This striking image is not just a visual feast, but also a powerful metaphor for the incredible resilience of nature. Like the scarab beetle, we too have the ability to draw strength from the most unlikely sources, and to emerge stronger and more radiant than before.
